BldgType - building type descriptor to differentiate single family, multifamily and potentially other types  (Proj:BldgTypeTblStr = 'SingleFam' or 'MultiFam')
Metric - description of run results this multiplier is being appied to (TDV vs. SourceEnergy vs. alternative metrics…)
HtgDRPFuelMult - multiplier on heating fuel TDV/SourceEnergy used only in calculating design ratings
ClgDRPFuelMult - multiplier on cooling fuel TDV/SourceEnergy used only in calculating design ratings
DHWDRPFuelMult - multiplier on DHW fuel TDV/SourceEnergy used only in calculating design ratings
AppDRPFuelMult - multiplier on appliance fuel TDV/SourceEnergy used only in calculating design ratings
